Programming note: As I mentioned yesterday, we=E2=80=99re trying a new Mone=
y Stuff podcast, in which my friend Katie Greifeld and I discuss the week i=
n the newsletter and financial news. If you like the newsletter but want mo=
re of it, in podcast form, check out the podcast.Our first episode is out n=
ow. This week, we discuss the Destiny Tech100 fund, the Mango Markets explo=
it and the Bureau of Labor Statistics inflation super users. Also there=E2=
=80=99s a reader creative-writing submission? It was fun. You can listen to=
 the episode here.
   =20


We=E2=80=99d love your feedback. You can email us at moneypod@bloomberg.net=
.You can get Money Stuff: The Podcast at Apple, Spotify or wherever you get=
 your podcasts. New episodes will come out on Fridays.Also, because people =
have asked: The podcast is just a fun extra thing we are doing. If you pref=
er your Money Stuff in traditional newsletter form, nothing=C2=A0will chang=
e for you. Except, I guess, that I am currently sending you this email.
